      <guid>http://localhost:1313/appunti/Analisi-T2/Spazi-vettoriali/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h3 id=&#34;prodotto-cartesiano-tra-due-insiemi&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Prodotto cartesiano tra due insiemi&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#prodotto-cartesiano-tra-due-insiemi&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;$$&#xA;\mathbb{A}_1 \times \mathbb{A}_2 = \{ (a_1, a_2) : a_1 \in \mathbb{A}_1, a_2 \in \mathbb{A}_2 \}&#xA;$$&lt;h3 id=&#34;coincidenza-di-due-coppie-cartesiane&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Coincidenza di due coppie cartesiane&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#coincidenza-di-due-coppie-cartesiane&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;$$&#xA;(a_1, a_2) = (a_3, a_4) \implies a_1 = a_3, a_2 = a_4&#xA;$$&lt;h3 id=&#34;insiemi-coincidenti&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Insiemi coincidenti&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#insiemi-coincidenti&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;$$&#xA;\mathbb{A}_1 \times \dots \times \mathbb{A}_n = \mathbb{A}^n&#xA;$$$$&#xA;\mathbb{R}^n = \{ (x_1, \dots, x_n) : x_1 \in \mathbb{R}, \dots, x_n \in \mathbb{R} \}&#xA;$$&lt;h3 id=&#34;somma-in&#34;&gt;&#xA;  Somma in $\mathbb{R}^n$&#xA;  &lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#somma-in&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt;&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&#xA;$$&#xA;(\mathbb{R}^n \times \mathbb{R}^n \to \mathbb{R}^n) = (x \times y \to x + y \in \mathbb{R}^n)&#xA;$$&lt;p&gt;&#xA;e.g.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
